%% Data Flow Diagram

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as Tauri UI
    participant Rust as Tauri Backend
    participant Python as FastAPI Sidecar
    participant Agent as Agent Core
    participant LLM as LLM Provider

    User->>UI: User sends message
    UI->>Rust: Tauri invoke (spawn sidecar)
    Rust->>Python: Start process if not running
    UI->>Python: HTTP POST /chat
    Python->>Agent: orchestrator.build_plan()
    Agent->>Python: detect.intent()
    Agent->>LLM: Classify intent
    LLM-->>Agent: Intent + tool selection
    Agent->>UI: SSE: plan preview
    UI->>User: Show plan, confirm?
    User->>UI: Approve
    UI->>Python: POST /execute
    Python->>Agent: executor.run_steps()
    Agent->>LLM: Execute with tools
    LLM-->>Agent: Tool use requests
    Agent->>Agent: permission_manager.check()
    Agent->>Python: tools.execute()
    Python-->>Agent: Tool results
    Agent->>LLM: Continue with tool results
    LLM-->>Agent: Final response
    Agent-->>UI: SSE: response chunks
    UI-->>User: Display response
    Agent->>Agent: chatstore.save()
```

