%% Execution Flow (Plan → Execute)

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: Start
    Idle --> Detect: User Input
    Detect --> Classify: Analyze Intent
    Classify --> PlanPreview: Build Plan
    Classify --> DirectChat: Simple Query
    PlanPreview --> WaitingApproval: Show Plan
    WaitingApproval --> Approved: User Approves
    WaitingApproval --> Rejected: User Rejects
    Rejected --> Idle
    Approved --> Executing: Execute Steps
    DirectChat --> Executing: Skip Planning
    Executing --> StepExecute: Each Step
    StepExecute --> PermissionCheck: Tool Use
    PermissionCheck --> ToolExecution: Approved
    PermissionCheck --> WaitingApproval: Denied
    ToolExecution --> StepComplete: Tool Result
    StepComplete --> Executing: More Steps?
    Executing --> Streaming: All Steps Done
    Streaming --> Idle: Complete
    Streaming --> Error: Exception
    Error --> Idle: Recover
```
